name: FeFoFall
description:
For reasons unexplained you must navigate through 110 short, single screen challenges that get steadily more complex and challenging. How many attempts will it take you to complete them all?

---

Use WASD / arrow keys for movement.

---

This game was created in about three weeks as part of a Game a Month challenge (profile here). My goal was to launch on multiple platforms and contain 100 or more levels.

I like this game and will probably expand it, so if anyone has any feedback let me know on Twitter @DziekDB or through bending railroads or whatever.
